title: Marketing budget
body: We want to propose first usage for the dev fund (20% of total ZOO supply) as a budget for our future marketing campaign. Paul, our marketing expert, can find usage for any amount we can get for him. It's up to community to decide how much of dev fund we can spend on marketing. Final percentage will be parked as maximum amount we can use on marketing and will be utilized partially on demand.
